        <p>
          Please contact us at (505) 792-1110 ext.1 or toll free in the US and Canada (855) 989-6824, use our online inquiry form, or emails us at sales@ideum.com. Our multitouch tables are sold domestically and internationally and are only available direct from Ideum.
